description:
The Avengers go head to head with the Hulk over their unfair hiring practices. With the help of She Hulk, the jade giant wages war on Iron Man, Captain America, Wasp and Thor. Can our mighty avengers come together to win this legal spat? Yeah kinda watch the vid, skip to the end if it's that important. Jeez.
